        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Parameter-Header">File-path</text> and <text styleclass="Parameter-Header">File-name</text> are now in boxes<image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image>.</para>
