                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">When you click the <link displaytype="button" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="MakeMovie-MakeMovie">Make Movie</link> button, the model moves the model to the <text styleclass="Parameter">Start-Angle</text> and compiles the movie (GIF file-type) or saves the images (PNG, JPG, BMP file-types)</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">Please <text styleclass="Interface2">wait</text> as we save for you the file(s) to your PC.</para>
              </td>
