                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">When you click the <link displaytype="button" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="MakeMovie-MakeMovie">Single Shot</link><text styleclass="Bullets"> button, you will save a Single Snapshot of the model at its active </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Master-Machine Angle</text><text styleclass="Bullets">.</text></para>
